rows.label: qst004003_msg0001
rows.name:
You want to know if I've seen
any suspicious individuals?

rows.label: qst004003_msg0002
rows.name:
My duty is to keep watch here! If
such an incident occurred, I would
have reported it immediately!

rows.label: qst004003_msg0004
rows.name:
The other night, a unit
returning from patrol in the
area was attacked by someone.

rows.label: qst004003_msg0005
rows.name:
Fortunately, the soldiers only
suffered minor scratches...

rows.label: qst004003_msg0006
rows.name:
But it's said that the
attackers had extremely
high marksmanship skills.

rows.label: qst004003_msg0007
rows.name:
Thanks to Superbia's contributions,
Gula is at peace, so that's the
only incident of note.

rows.label: qst004003_msg0101
rows.name:
Bows, you say...? Primitive, but
it certainly keeps costs down.

rows.label: qst004003_msg0102
rows.name:
Managing expenses is also my
responsibility... a difficult task...
